message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you an exclusive opportunity to acquire our premium product. Given the exceptional quality and value it brings, I'm setting the price at $1500000. I believe this figure represents both the excellence of the product and the unique benefits it offers. I look forward to your thoughts on this proposal.

Hi Alice, thank you for the offer. While I appreciate the quality of the product, I have a budget constraint. I am willing to purchase it for $500000. Please let me know if we can work towards a mutually beneficial agreement.
